                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>Henry S. Villard, Deputy Director of the Office of Near Eastern and African
                    Affairs, delivered an address on “Some Aspects of Our Policy in Greece and
                    Turkey” at Charlotte, North Carolina, on May 5; for text, see Department of
                    State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, May 18, 1947, page 997.</p>
            </div>
